markdown: <::A black and white photograph shows a wine glass filled with red wine. The upper part of the glass is etched with two floral patterns, each resembling a stylized rose with a square center and radiating petals. The glass has a clear stem and a round base. A knife with a curved blade and a decorative handle is lying horizontally behind the base of the glass, partially visible.: figure::> <::A silver serving tray with ornate, scrolled handles on each end. The tray has a scalloped edge and an engraved, swirling pattern covering its surface. The tray is rectangular with rounded, wavy sides.: figure::> <::A two-panel image. The left panel shows a glass flask containing a dark liquid, placed in front of an old map of the world. The map shows "AMERICA" and "TERRA NOVA". The right panel shows a champagne bottle, labeled "QUALITY", chilling in an ice bucket filled with ice cubes. The ice bucket is white with a floral pattern and has two small handles.: figure::> 16 Source: https://www.industrydocuments.ucsf.edu/docs/njnp0227
